  m_text: "Welcome to Lama Rama Fish Co. \nYou have been tasked to rescue fish that
    have wondered up on the banks and are injured. \n\nYou have collect them and
    place them in tanks. \nFeed them \U0001F357. \nMake them feel comfortable \U0001F6CB\uFE0F
    by sharing the tank with fish from the same area and items from the same area
    BUT not too many!. \n\nOnce they are fully healed up at full Health \U0001F497you
    can release them back to their home!\n\nReady to start your job?"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 32fc6e1220a8bf14b84e00f32deb9a23, type: 2}
